        <h2 id="Who-can-use-the-service" class="govuk-heading-m">
          How to access the service
          </h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">Your organisation must have a Defra account to use the Report receipt of waste service.</p>

        <p class="govuk-body">You will need to:</p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
          <li>Create a Government Gateway or OneLogin account for your organisation or sign in if you already have one.</li>
          <li>Use your organisation's Government Gateway or OneLogin ID to register for a Defra account.</li>
          <li>Pay the service charge &#40;not due until October 2026&#41;</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="govuk-warning-text">
